data.description: Welcome to 3310 Shamrock Place!  Beautiful home featuring 4 bedrooms with 2 full bathrooms tucked in a wonderful neighborhood within walking distance to Rahilly Park. Lots of remodeling has been completed with beautiful finishes and thoughtful planning. Newer sliding glass door added for easy access to the pool area,  plus new dual pane windows throughout.  Fabulous backyard with in ground, gunite pool and an outdoor lounge area equipped with TV that is (included in this sale) mounted on the exterior wall. Extra cement path added to driveway area. This is a must see home in a great location.
